{"tid":1200211,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黑 色 洋 紫 荊 Black Blakeana","createTime":"2019-06-10T16:50:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T16:41:40.000Z","uid":154486,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5f43026951c53df2963e33f8be5719cb38b839a3","tid":1200211,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T16:50:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/11/004757_3790bb6ec98a3e98bb087ab8714a524d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F11%2F004757_3790bb6ec98a3e98bb087ab8714a524d.png&h=503ace9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n洋紫荊（學名：Bauhinia&nbsp;&times;&nbsp;<span style=\"color: red;\">blakeana</span>[1][2]），别名香港蘭（英语：Hong Kong Orchid Tree），是豆科羊蹄甲屬的有花植物，於香港首次發現，並獲定為香港市花。<br />\n<br />\n洋紫荊的拉丁文學名的种加詞命名為 'Blakeana'，以紀念熱愛研究植物的<strong>第12任香港總督卜力</strong>（Sir Henry Arthur BLAKE）伉儷。"},{"pid":"d4d036d5454c5e9f70dcce40ac120234d39c1e12","tid":1200211,"uid":154486,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T16:51:49.000Z","msg":"我地終於有名啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f84afe6eca42c199bb8c99fb65aed38be2915c64","tid":1200211,"uid":154486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T17:10:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78737776eeeafdb0ceff931523b1780912c3a108","tid":1200211,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T23:24:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"192db9e2efba0a2373c3cb26e6edfea7a6d57451","tid":1200211,"uid":5150,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:03:20.000Z","msg":"傳呢張圖可能俾人砌區旗法<br />\n不如用市政局或者金管局洋紫荊嘅黑色版"},{"pid":"e8f118a9e6f0fce579b0268fda018667f3bb3c24","tid":1200211,"uid":60393,"like":0,"dislike"